snippet.title: Sicherman Dice (Tanton Mathematics)
snippet.description:
What is the probability of rolling a 7, or a 2, or a 5, or a ... with ordinary dice? What is the probability of rolling a 7, or a 2, or a 5, or a ... with Sicherman dice? The same!
Here's a lovely renumbering system of dice.
